author: Kam Dhillon
title: Feast Your Eyes on Some Fresh Sneaker Heat From Prague Fashion Week
text:
Visit the original post to see all 20 images from this gallery. 
Location: Prague, Czech Republic
Season: Fall/Winter 2017
Key Looks: DIY steez at its finest (slide #1), Raf Simons x adidas Ozweego Bunny in cream (slide #5), and that sleek Y-3 silhouette (slide #7),
Editor’s Notes: Our latest street style hones focus on some of the most fire kicks worn on the streets of Prague, and as expected, it’s a diverse offering of all the trending sneakers currently on rotation.
You’ve seen what Prague wears down low, now check out the city’s finest street style from Mercedes-Benz Prague Fashion Week .
